      <akn:section eId="sec_31_5031_03">
        <akn:num>31-5031.03</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Authorized activities of title insurers.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-5031_03_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Engage in the business of writing title insurance directly or through title insurance producers appointed for the purpose of issuing policies of title insurance;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-5031_03_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Reinsure title insurance policies;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-5031_03_3">
      <akn:num>(3)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Unless prohibited by the Commissioner, perform ancillary activities, including examining titles to real property and any interest in real or personal property and procuring and furnishing related information and information about relevant personal property, when not in contemplation of, or in conjunction with, the issuance of a title insurance policy; and</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-5031_03_4">
      <akn:num>(4)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Maintain or perform escrow, indemnity, or settlement services.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
